5.1 Finance: The Vanguard of Automation

Finance was an early adopter of AI and remains the most mature sector for agent deployment. The reasons are clear: finance runs on data, operates under clear rules, and has well-defined success metrics. It is, in many ways, the ideal environment for agents.

