5.3.3 The Pattern: Human in the Loop, Always

Healthcare has settled on a clear pattern: agents augment, but humans decide. Every clinical agent includes explicit handoffs to human clinicians at critical junctures. Every patient-facing agent makes clear that it is an AI, not a doctor. The human-in-the-loop is not a fallback; it is the architecture.

5.3.4 Challenges

